casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Steffen. Cincinnati Bar Association v. Steffen.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Steffen (1993), 67 Ohio St.3d 1207.]

(Nos. 93-1828 and 93-869 Submitted September 21, 1993 Decided September 22, 1993.)

The resignation of Albert J. Steffen of Cincinnati, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0020940, is accepted; sua sponte, case No. 93-869, Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Steffen, is dismissed as moot, with costs to respondent.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. F.E. Sweeney, J., dissents.
